    :meth:`Gdk.Texture.new_from_resource`,
    :meth:`Gdk.Texture.new_from_bytes`,
    :meth:`Gdk.Texture.new_from_file`,
    :meth:`Gdk.Texture.new_from_filename`,
    :meth:`Gdk.Texture.new_for_pixbuf`. Note that these are meant for loading
    icons and resources that are shipped with the toolkit or application. It
    is recommended that you use a dedicated image loading framework such as
    `glycin <https://lib.rs/crates/glycin>`_, if you need to load untrusted image
    data.
